{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012svBsZsEQhEHBour62rcPc","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Specification: 008 User Profile\n2\t\n3\t## Meta\n4\t\n5\t| Field | Value |\n6\t|-------|-------|\n7\t| Status | Ready |\n8\t| Priority | P1 |\n9\t| Phase | 3 |\n10\t| NR_OF_TRIES | 13 |\n11\t\n12\t---\n13\t\n14\t## Overview\n15\t\n16\tPlayer profile system for TAUNT. Backend/API only — no frontend work in this\n17\tspec. The profile is the player's identity on the platform: a username, avatar,\n18\taggregate stats, and transaction history. Wallets are never exposed publicly;\n19\tall external-facing lookups use a short user ID or username.\n20\t\n21\t**Iteration 1 (done):** Transaction history ledger + API.\n22\t\n23\t**Iteration 2 (this pass):** Player identity (profile record, username, avatar),\n24\taggregate stats, public lookup API, HEAT/points display slots (null until those\n25\tfeatures ship).\n26\t\n27\tNo on-chain footprint. No social accounts (X/Discord) — deferred TBD.\n28\t\n29\t## User Stories\n30\t\n31\t- As a player, I want to see every game transaction tied to my wallet so I can\n32\t  track what I wagered, won, or lost.\n33\t- As a player, I want the list to update automatically after a game settles so\n34\t  I don't have to refresh.\n35\t- As a player, I want an auto-generated username when I sign up so I have an\n36\t  identity on the platform immediately.\n37\t- As a player, I want to change my username so I can personalize my identity,\n38\t  with a cooldown to prevent abuse.\n39\t- As a player, I want to see my aggregate stats (games played, wins, win rate,\n40\t  streaks) so I can track my performance.\n41\t- As another player, I want to look up someone by username or ID and see their\n42\t  public stats (games played, wins, win rate) without seeing their wallet or\n43\t  transaction history.\n44\t\n45\t---\n46\t\n47\t## Scope Alignment\n48\t\n49\t- **`docs/SCOPE.md` references**: Phase 3 — \"Basic player profile/history from\n50\t  indexed data\"; Launch checklist — \"Basic profile/history available and\n51\t  accurate\"\n52\t- **Scope status**: V1 In Scope\n53\t- **Phase boundary**: Phase 3\n54\t\n55\t## Required Context Files\n56\t\n57\t- `services/backend/src/db.ts` — DB client & query functions\n58\t- `services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts` — settlement write path (coinflip + lord)\n59\t- `services/backend/src/worker/closecall-clock.ts` — closecall settlement write path (settleRound function)\n60\t- `services/backend/src/routes/` — existing route patterns\n61\t- `services/backend/migrations/` — migration files (see Developer Reference below)\n62\t- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/` — mock profile system + components\n63\t\n64\t## Contract Files\n65\t\n66\t- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/types.ts` — `ProfileTransaction` type (frontend shape)\n67\t- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx` — table component to wire\n68\t\n69\t---\n70\t\n71\t## Functional Requirements\n72\t\n73\t### FR-1: `user_transactions` Ledger Table\n74\t\n75\tA new PostgreSQL table that stores one row per user-visible game event.\n76\t\n77\t**Schema:**\n78\t\n79\t| Column | Type | Constraints | Notes |\n80\t|--------|------|-------------|-------|\n81\t| `id` | `BIGSERIAL` | PK | Auto-increment |\n82\t| `wallet` | `TEXT` | NOT NULL | Player wallet address |\n83\t| `game` | `TEXT` | NOT NULL | `coinflip`, `lord`, `closecall` |\n84\t| `match_id` | `TEXT` | NOT NULL | Links to rounds/closecall_rounds |\n85\t| `event` | `TEXT` | NOT NULL | `join`, `win`, `loss`, `refund` |\n86\t| `amount_lamports` | `BIGINT` | NOT NULL | Wager (join) or payout (win) or refund amount |\n87\t| `tx_sig` | `TEXT` | | On-chain transaction signature (nullable until confirmed) |\n88\t| `created_at` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | NOT NULL DEFAULT now() | Event timestamp |\n89\t\n90\t**Indexes:**\n91\t- `idx_user_tx_wallet_created` on `(wallet, created_at DESC)` — paginated history\n92\t- `idx_user_tx_match_id` on `(match_id)` — dedup / lookup\n93\t\n94\t**Acceptance Criteria:**\n95\t- [x] Migration `007_user_transactions.sql` creates the table and indexes <!-- satisfied: migrations/008_user_transactions.sql:1-30 (named 008 because 007 was taken) — table, 2 indexes, UNIQUE constraint -->\n96\t- [x] Migration runs cleanly on a fresh DB and on an existing DB <!-- satisfied: standard IF NOT EXISTS DDL pattern; confirmed in history iterations 1 + 11 -->\n97\t- [x] No backfill of historical data (table starts empty) <!-- satisfied: migrations/008_user_transactions.sql contains only DDL, no INSERT/UPDATE -->\n98\t\n99\t### FR-2: Write Path — Populate on Settlement\n100\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"997cbca0-e18d-4fe1-a187-4ae4b9c08df2","uuid":"f567fb30-bb33-49ca-b733-595ef9e9f69f","timestamp":"2026-03-31T14:06:37.414Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/008-user-profile/spec.md","content":"# Specification: 008 User Profile\n\n## Meta\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Status | Ready |\n| Priority | P1 |\n| Phase | 3 |\n| NR_OF_TRIES | 13 |\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nPlayer profile system for TAUNT. Backend/API only — no frontend work in this\nspec. The profile is the player's identity on the platform: a username, avatar,\naggregate stats, and transaction history. Wallets are never exposed publicly;\nall external-facing lookups use a short user ID or username.\n\n**Iteration 1 (done):** Transaction history ledger + API.\n\n**Iteration 2 (this pass):** Player identity (profile record, username, avatar),\naggregate stats, public lookup API, HEAT/points display slots (null until those\nfeatures ship).\n\nNo on-chain footprint. No social accounts (X/Discord) — deferred TBD.\n\n## User Stories\n\n- As a player, I want to see every game transaction tied to my wallet so I can\n  track what I wagered, won, or lost.\n- As a player, I want the list to update automatically after a game settles so\n  I don't have to refresh.\n- As a player, I want an auto-generated username when I sign up so I have an\n  identity on the platform immediately.\n- As a player, I want to change my username so I can personalize my identity,\n  with a cooldown to prevent abuse.\n- As a player, I want to see my aggregate stats (games played, wins, win rate,\n  streaks) so I can track my performance.\n- As another player, I want to look up someone by username or ID and see their\n  public stats (games played, wins, win rate) without seeing their wallet or\n  transaction history.\n\n---\n\n## Scope Alignment\n\n- **`docs/SCOPE.md` references**: Phase 3 — \"Basic player profile/history from\n  indexed data\"; Launch checklist — \"Basic profile/history available and\n  accurate\"\n- **Scope status**: V1 In Scope\n- **Phase boundary**: Phase 3\n\n## Required Context Files\n\n- `services/backend/src/db.ts` — DB client & query functions\n- `services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts` — settlement write path (coinflip + lord)\n- `services/backend/src/worker/closecall-clock.ts` — closecall settlement write path (settleRound function)\n- `services/backend/src/routes/` — existing route patterns\n- `services/backend/migrations/` — migration files (see Developer Reference below)\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/` — mock profile system + components\n\n## Contract Files\n\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/types.ts` — `ProfileTransaction` type (frontend shape)\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx` — table component to wire\n\n---\n\n## Functional Requirements\n\n### FR-1: `user_transactions` Ledger Table\n\nA new PostgreSQL table that stores one row per user-visible game event.\n\n**Schema:**\n\n| Column | Type | Constraints | Notes |\n|--------|------|-------------|-------|\n| `id` | `BIGSERIAL` | PK | Auto-increment |\n| `wallet` | `TEXT` | NOT NULL | Player wallet address |\n| `game` | `TEXT` | NOT NULL | `coinflip`, `lord`, `closecall` |\n| `match_id` | `TEXT` | NOT NULL | Links to rounds/closecall_rounds |\n| `event` | `TEXT` | NOT NULL | `join`, `win`, `loss`, `refund` |\n| `amount_lamports` | `BIGINT` | NOT NULL | Wager (join) or payout (win) or refund amount |\n| `tx_sig` | `TEXT` | | On-chain transaction signature (nullable until confirmed) |\n| `created_at` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | NOT NULL DEFAULT now() | Event timestamp |\n\n**Indexes:**\n- `idx_user_tx_wallet_created` on `(wallet, created_at DESC)` — paginated history\n- `idx_user_tx_match_id` on `(match_id)` — dedup / lookup\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [x] Migration `007_user_transactions.sql` creates the table and indexes <!-- satisfied: migrations/008_user_transactions.sql:1-30 (named 008 because 007 was taken) — table, 2 indexes, UNIQUE constraint -->\n- [x] Migration runs cleanly on a fresh DB and on an existing DB <!-- satisfied: standard IF NOT EXISTS DDL pattern; confirmed in history iterations 1 + 11 -->\n- [x] No backfill of historical data (table starts empty) <!-- satisfied: migrations/008_user_transactions.sql contains only DDL, no INSERT/UPDATE -->\n\n### FR-2: Write Path — Populate on Settlement\n","numLines":100,"startLine":1,"totalLines":684}}}
